                                <ns0:p>Letters are extremely regular and neat, with letter heights all identical (except for phi in line 1, which extends above the guideline). Letters are thin, tall and evenly spaced. Terminal dots carved on all letters. Use of the classic zeta in line 2.</ns0:p>
                                <ns0:locus from="line1" to="line3">Lines 1-3</ns0:locus>
